title: Campout Pre Party feat. ALRT
description:
Welcome to the Official San Francisco Campout Music Festival Preparty hosted by Dirty Not Sorry!

## Headliner:

### ►ALRT

[Alrt.komi.io](http://alrt.komi.io/)

Throughout the genre infusion, ALRT has pinpointed his “NRG” movement to be an inspiring feeling no matter the genre of choice. Having released on ULTRA, Musical Freedom, Deadbeats, STMPD, SONY, Confession, Gud Vibrations, Dim Mak, Insomniac, Universal, Welcome, and more. It is clear he has established himself as one of the most highly sought after producers around. Praised by DJ Mag as one of “the latest and greatest DJs and producers rising to the top”, ALRT has continued to catch attention with anything he releases.
